---
import { base } from "astro:config/server";

import Title from "../ui/Title.astro";
import Text from "../ui/Text.astro";
---

<section id="vision-and-mission">
   <div class="auto-margin">
      <div id="vision-and-mission-mission">
         <div id="vision-and-mission-mission-icon-container">
            <img src={`${base}icons/rocket-primary.png`} alt="" />
         </div>
         <Title type="h4">Nuestra misión</Title>
         <Text
            >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quo modi omnis nisi similique! Neque quis eius,
            rerum eos quod saepe deleniti ab ratione ex nam. Natus commodi ducimus ipsum temporibus incidunt. Ipsa a
            laudantium error sequi ipsum incidunt.</Text
         >
      </div>
      <div id="vision-and-mission-vision">
         <div id="vision-and-mission-vision-icon-container">
            <img src={`${base}icons/eye.png`} alt="" />
         </div>
         <Title type="h4">Nuestra visión</Title>
         <Text
            >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quo modi omnis nisi similique! Neque quis eius,
            rerum eos quod saepe deleniti ab ratione ex nam. Natus commodi ducimus ipsum temporibus incidunt. Ipsa a
            laudantium error sequi ipsum incidunt.</Text
         >
      </div>
   </div>
</section>

<style>
   #vision-and-mission {
      height: fit-content;
      padding-block: var(--gap-sections);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: var(--background-dark-color);

      .auto-margin {
         display: flex;
         flex-direction: column;
         align-items: stretch;
         gap: var(--gap-cards);

         #vision-and-mission-mission,
         #vision-and-mission-vision {
            height: 400px;
            padding: var(--gap-cards);
            border-radius: var(--rounded-base);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
         }

         #vision-and-mission-mission-icon-container,
         #vision-and-mission-vision-icon-container {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: var(--rounded-base);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: var(--background-dark-color);

            img {
               width: 32px;
            }
         }
      }
   }

   @media screen and (min-width: 1280px) {
      #vision-and-mission {
         .auto-margin {
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: var(--gap-sections);

            #vision-and-mission-mission {
               width: 50%;
            }

            #vision-and-mission-vision {
               width: 50%;
            }
         }
      }
   }
</style>
